#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/03_basicmodel.rst:113
msgid "Add a ``_description`` to your model to get rid of one of the warnings."
msgstr "Warning တစ်ခုကို ဖယ်ရှားရန် သင့် model ထဲသို့ ``_description`` ထည့်ပါ။"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/03_basicmodel.rst:116
msgid "Model fields"
msgstr "Model field များ"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/03_basicmodel.rst:119
msgid ""
"**Reference**: the documentation related to this topic can be found in the "
":ref:`reference/orm/fields` API."
msgstr ""
"**Reference**: ဤ topic နှင့် သက်ဆိုင်သော documentation ကို :ref:`reference/orm/fields` API တွင် "
