msgid "cancel or set a property as sold"
msgstr "property တစ်ခုကို cancel လုပ်ရန် သို့မဟုတ် sold အဖြစ် သတ်မှတ်ရန်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/09_actions.rst:11
msgid "accept or refuse an offer"
msgstr "offer တစ်ခုကို accept သို့မဟုတ် refuse လုပ်ရန်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/09_actions.rst:13
msgid ""
"One could argue that we can already do these things by changing the state manually, but this is "
