#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:484
msgid "Every time the partner name is changed, the description is modified."
msgstr "Partner name ပြောင်းလဲတိုင်း description ကို ပြင်ဆင်သည်။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:486
