msgstr "Property ၏ state သည် 'New' သို့မဟုတ် 'Cancelled' မဟုတ်ပါက delete လုပ်ခြင်းကို တားပါ"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:92
msgid ""
"Tip: create a new method with the :func:`~odoo.api.ondelete` decorator and remember that ``self``"
