#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:178
msgid ""
"Instead of modifying existing views in place (by overwriting them), Odoo provides view "
"inheritance where children 'extension' views are applied on top of root views. These extension "
"can both add and remove content from their parent view."
msgstr ""
"ရှိပြီးသား view များကို place ထဲတွင် ပြင်ခြင်း (overwrite လုပ်ခြင်း) အစား Odoo သည် root view "
"များပေါ်တွင် child “extension” view များကို apply လုပ်သော view inheritance ကို ပေးသည်။ ဤ "
"extension များသည် parent view မှ content ထည့်နိုင်သလို ဖယ်နိုင်သည်။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:182
msgid ""
"An extension view references its parent using the ``inherit_id`` field. Instead of a single view,"
" its ``arch`` field contains a number of ``xpath`` elements that select and alter the content of "
"their parent view:"
msgstr ""
"Extension view သည် ``inherit_id`` field ကို အသုံးပြု၍ parent ကို ရည်ညွှန်းသည်။ Single view "
"တစ်ခုအစား ၎င်း၏ ``arch`` field တွင် parent view ၏ content ကို ရွေးချယ်ပြီး ပြင်ဆင်သော ``xpath`` "
"element အရေအတွက်တစ်ခု ပါသည်။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:202
msgid "``expr``"
msgstr "``expr``"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:202
msgid ""
"An XPath_ expression selecting a single element in the parent view. Raises an error if it matches"
" no element or more than one"
msgstr ""
"Parent view ထဲရှိ single element တစ်ခုကို ရွေးချယ်သော XPath_ expression ဖြစ်သည်။ Element မတွေ့ပါက"
" သို့မဟုတ် တစ်ခုထက်ပိုတွေ့ပါက error တင်သည်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:218
msgid "``position``"
msgstr "``position``"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:205
msgid "Operation to apply to the matched element:"
msgstr "Matched element ပေါ်တွင် apply လုပ်မည့် operation ဖြစ်သည်။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:207
msgid "``inside``"
msgstr "``inside``"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:208
msgid "appends ``xpath``'s body to the end of the matched element"
msgstr "``xpath`` ၏ body ကို matched element ၏ အဆုံးတွင် append လုပ်သည်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:210
msgid "``replace``"
msgstr "``replace``"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:210
msgid ""
"replaces the matched element with the ``xpath``'s body, replacing any ``$0`` node occurrence in "
"the new body with the original element"
msgstr ""
"Matched element ကို ``xpath`` ၏ body ဖြင့် replace လုပ်ပြီး body အသစ်ထဲရှိ ``$0`` node occurrence"
" မည်သည်မဆို original element ဖြင့် replace လုပ်သည်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:212
msgid "``before``"
msgstr "``before``"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:213
msgid "inserts the ``xpath``'s body as a sibling before the matched element"
msgstr "``xpath`` ၏ body ကို matched element ၏ အရှေ့ sibling အဖြစ် insert လုပ်သည်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:214
msgid "``after``"
msgstr "``after``"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:215
msgid "inserts the ``xpaths``'s body as a sibling after the matched element"
msgstr "``xpaths`` ၏ body ကို matched element ၏ အနောက် sibling အဖြစ် insert လုပ်သည်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:218
msgid "``attributes``"
msgstr "``attributes``"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:217
msgid ""
"alters the attributes of the matched element using the special ``attribute`` elements in the "
"``xpath``'s body"
msgstr ""
"``xpath`` body ထဲရှိ special ``attribute`` element များကို အသုံးပြု၍ matched element ၏ attribute "
"များကို ပြင်သည်"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:220
msgid ""
"When matching a single element, the ``position`` attribute can be set directly on the element to "
"be found. Both inheritances below have the same result."
msgstr ""
"Single element တစ်ခုကို match လုပ်သောအခါ ``position`` attribute ကို ရှာမည့် element ပေါ်တွင် "
"တိုက်ရိုက်သတ်မှတ်နိုင်သည်။ အောက်ပါ inheritance နှစ်ခုလုံးသည် result တူညီသည်။"

